{"text_id":182534,"tokens":["Driver","less"," cars",","," also"," known"," as"," autonomous"," vehicles",","," have"," been"," a"," topic"," of"," great"," interest"," and"," debate"," in"," recent"," years","."," With"," advances"," in"," technology",","," these"," vehicles"," have"," the"," potential"," to"," revolution","ize"," the"," way"," we"," travel"," and"," live","."," However",","," there"," are"," also"," significant"," concerns"," regarding"," the"," safety",","," efficiency",","," and"," practicality"," of"," driver","less"," cars","."," In"," this"," essay",","," I"," will"," discuss"," the"," pros"," and"," cons"," of"," driver","less"," cars"," and"," argue"," whether"," they"," should"," be"," further"," developed"," until"," the"," positives"," clearly"," outweigh"," the"," negatives",".","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," most"," significant"," benefits"," of"," driver","less"," cars"," is"," the"," potential"," for"," increased"," safety","."," According"," to"," the"," National"," Highway"," Traffic"," Safety"," Administration"," (","NH","TSA","),"," human"," error"," is"," a"," contributing"," factor"," in"," ","9","0","%"," of"," crashes","."," Autonomous"," vehicles",","," on"," the"," other"," hand",","," are"," not"," subject"," to"," the"," same"," limitations"," as"," human"," drivers",","," such"," as"," distraction",","," impairment",","," or"," fatigue","."," Additionally",","," driver","less"," cars"," can"," communicate"," with"," each"," other",","," allowing"," for"," a"," more"," efficient"," flow"," of"," traffic"," and"," potentially"," reducing"," the"," number"," of"," accidents",".","\n\n","Another"," advantage"," of"," driver","less"," cars"," is"," their"," potential"," to"," increase"," efficiency","."," By"," removing"," the"," human"," element"," from"," driving",","," vehicles"," can"," be"," designed"," to"," operate"," at"," optimal"," speeds",","," reducing"," congestion"," and"," saving"," time","."," Furthermore",","," a